  "title": "sales interior designer",
  "description": "<p>Job Openings: Sales-Oriented Interior Designers (Team Members & Team Leaders)</p><p>About Us:</p><p>We specialize in customized whole-home cabinetry, focusing on environmentally friendly and precision woodwork. Join our team to bring high-quality, sustainable designs to life for our valued clients.</p><p>Positions Available:</p><p>1. Team Member (Sales Designer)</p><p>2. Team Leader (Sales Design Supervisor)</p><p>Job Responsibilities:</p><p>• Engage with clients to understand their needs and provide tailored interior design solutions.</p><p>• Actively promote and sell customized cabinetry and woodwork solutions to clients.</p><p>• Create design proposals, including detailed layouts and 3D renderings, using design software.</p><p>• Coordinate and communicate with production teams to ensure client expectations are met.</p><p>• Lead and manage a team of designers (for Team Leaders), ensuring project goals and sales targets are achieved.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• Proven sales experience with a strong ability to close deals.</p><p>• Interior design expertise, including space planning, materials selection, and 3D design tools (e.g., AutoCAD, SketchUp).</p><p>• Passion for environmentally friendly and high-quality craftsmanship.</p><p>• Excellent communication and interpersonal skills to build rapport with clients.</p><p>• For Team Leaders: Experience managing and motivating a team to achieve sales and design goals.</p><p>Work Schedule:</p><p>• 6-day workweek, 10 hours per day. 7 day annual leave and 7 day sick leave</p><p>Compensation & Benefits:</p><p>• Competitive salary based on experience and position.</p><p>• Commission opportunities based on sales performance.</p><p>• Career growth opportunities in a dynamic and supportive team environment.</p><p>Location:</p><p>• Singapore</p><p>How to Apply:</p><p>Send your resume and portfolio. Please indicate whether you are applying for the WhatsApp 80339179</p><p>Join us and make a difference in sustainable interior design!</p>",
